Node "4"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Oh yeah? Why’s that?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I heard you were having some problems, I might be able to help." linkto "Node_5"  notes "Quest seed from Jonathan"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I… uh… Raiders! Yeah, I saw a whole bunch of them coming this way. I have to warn your leader." linkto "2b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "My home and its people are in terrible danger. I must find what’s left of the GAI headquarters, and I think someone here might know where it is." linkto "2b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I just do. What’s this going to cost me?" linkto "20"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Never mind." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "5"
notes ""
{
NPCText "You heard what? Oh, you mean the AutoDoc. Yeah, that’s been broken for a while now. Damn thing won’t even switch on properly, it just click-click-clicks like a rat with a stutter."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I think I know the problem. If it’s a simple servomotor disjunction, it won’t take much to fix." linkto "11"  notes "[Sci/Repair]"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hmm… sounds like the flanking ring-valves are out of synch." linkto "7"  notes "[Bluff]"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "It’s probably just a faulty lip on the mainboard unit casing." linkto "7"  notes "[Bluff]"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Clicks? Have you checked for beetles?" linkto "6"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I wouldn't know how to fix that." linkto "56"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "6"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Beetles? Are you stupid?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No, I’m serious! Certain beetle species have been known to colonize electromechanical environments, with devastating results." linkto "7a"  notes "[Tuff bluff]"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I’m only trying to help." linkto "-1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Never mind." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "7"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Sounds serious."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Oh, it is. I wouldn’t trust anybody without the proper knowledge and experience to repair it." linkto "8"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "It’s easily fixed if you know what you’re doing." linkto "8"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "It’s out of my depth, that’s for sure. I’ll be leaving." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "8"
notes ""
{
NPCText "And I suppose you’re just the man we’re looking for, turned up out of nowhere just like that."
 NPCFemaleText "And I suppose you’re just the sweet thing we’re looking for, turned up out of nowhere just like that."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Exactly. You should consider yourselves lucky I showed up when I did." linkto "10"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I’m just someone that happens to have the right tools for the job." linkto "11b"  notes "Medium speech check"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually, I was making that up. I have no idea how to fix it." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_FullofShit"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Oh yeah? Well I’ll make a deal with you. I’ll stop being negative when you stop being full of shit."
 NPCFemaleText "Oh yeah? Well I’ll make a deal with you, missy. I’ll stop being negative when you stop being full of shit."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[END]" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "10"
notes ""
{
NPCText "I guess we should."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So, are you going to let me through?" linkto "3b"  notes "[int<7]"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "And yet you’re still in my way." linkto "33"  notes "[int>7]"
              }
}
Node "11"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Yeah, that’s what the Doc said, something like that. You know about that kind of stuff?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Yeah, we used to get this sort of thing all the time back home. Just give me half an hour with it." linkto "13"  notes "[Bluff/Repair]"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I know a little. I couldn’t make any promises without a closer look." linkto "12"  notes "Repair skill check here"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why can’t the Doc fix it? He knows what the problem is. " linkto "14"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Whatever I know, I’m keeping it to myself. Goodbye. " linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "11b"
notes ""
{
NPCText "The Doc said something about servo-disfunction or something. Disjunction, disfunction, something like that. You know anything about that?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Yeah, we used to get this sort of thing all the time back home. Just give me half an hour with it." linkto "13"  notes "[Bluff/Repair]"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I know a little. I couldn’t make any promises without a closer look." linkto "12"  notes "Repair skill check here"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Nothing at all. I had some other questions." linkto "Node_6"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Whatever I know, I’m keeping it to myself. Goodbye. " linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "12"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Hmm… [he eyes you up and down] You can go in, but don’t try anything stupid. Head down and see the Doc."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll do that. " linkto "done"  notes " "
              }
}
Node "13"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Big words… you got your half-hour, but that’s it. You take one wrong step down there, I'll be the one kicking your ass."
 NPCFemaleText "Tall talk, missy... you got your half-hour. But you make one wrong move, don't think I won't be there to kick your ass."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll be good, I promise." linkto "done"  notes " After exiting dialogue -> npc floats ‘Take over, Barney, I’m going down to see Doc’ "
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I’ve changed my mind. I’ll come back later." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_SandoverRads"
notes ""
{
NPCText "What the hell do you think? This is poisoned earth we’re living on – not just us, everybody. It’ll get you too, in the end."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No point in worrying about it then, I guess. " linkto "Node_Sandover5"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "If this is a radiation hotspot, why live here?" linkto "Node_Sandover10"  notes "[Science]"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I had another question about Sandover." linkto "Node_Sandover"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Sandover5"
notes ""
{
NPCText "I guess not. Anything else?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I had some other questions." linkto "Node_Questions"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That's it. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Sandover10"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Where the fuck else are we going to live? It’s not like you can get away from it. Might as well stay where the scrap pays the highest."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "But there are better places than this!" linkto "Node_Sandover11"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I guess… where do you all come from, originally?" linkto "Node_Sandover12"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You’ve got a point, but I still think you’re better off somewhere else." linkto "Node_Notalk"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Sandover11"
notes ""
{
NPCText "That’s right – and when you get thrown out of all those places, you come here. Welcome to Sandover. Now, are you going to ask another stupid question, or are you going to move the fuck along?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I’m going to ask another stupid question." linkto "Node_Questions"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Your attitude is really starting to get to me. " linkto "Node_FullofShit"  notes " *BB"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I’ll leave you to it." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "20"
notes ""
{
NPCText "You really want to get in there? You gotta pay the toll. 100 caps."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Deal. [hand over the caps]" linkto "done"  notes "triggers ‘Knock yourself out’ floater"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How about 50?" linkto "-3"  notes "(result depends on barter skill) Needs a procedure to check barter and call the appropriate node."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Wait a minute – you just told me there was no way I was getting in. Now there’s a ‘standard price’?" linkto "21"  notes "*BB [NIEE] "
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe I could pay another way." linkto "Node_5"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you something first." linkto "Node_6"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Forget it." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "21"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Maybe I was trying to save you the disappointment. Maybe I just don’t like the way you look. You want in or not?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Fine. [hand over the caps]" linkto "done"  notes "done + ‘Knock yourself out’ floater"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How about 50?" linkto "-3"  notes "[Hard Barter]"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I want to ask something first." linkto "Node_6"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe I can pay another way..." linkto "Node_5"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Forget it." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Scab"
notes ""
{
NPCText "A Scab is a person I let down these caves. You don't get to go down there, so you're not a Scab. Get it?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Your logic is circular." linkto "Node_Noentry2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What if I pay you?" linkto "20"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I guess I'll be leaving." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Funee"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Hah! Good one. And here I was thinking you were an asshole."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks… I think. Can I ask you something else?" linkto "Node_Questions"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "24"
notes ""
{
NPCText "That’s one way of putting it. Most of us didn’t have a choice."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You mean you were thrown out? Out of where?" linkto "Node_Sandover12"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Well, beggars can’t be choosers." linkto "Node_Sandover5"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Sandover12"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Nowhere in particular. Few from here, few from there. Ain’t a settlement in the world doesn’t have its undesirables, even fewer that don’t jump at the first chance to get rid of them."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hmm… You know, I think I can relate to that." linkto "Node_Goodforyou"  notes "[>int]"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Great, a town populated by the dregs of the dregs. I can’t wait." linkto "Node_Sandover6"  notes " *BB"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What about you? Where did you come from?" linkto "Node_SamHistory"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That sounds about right. I had some other questions" linkto "Node_Questions"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Sandover6"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Keep talking, kid. You might never leave."
 NPCFemaleText "Keep it up, lady. Might be the last place you ever see."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have a few more questions." linkto "Node_Questions"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I don't take well to idle threats." linkto "Node_010"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[done]" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Goodforyou"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Good for you. Now, what do you want?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have another question." linkto "Node_Questions"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Never mind. I’ll have a look around for myself. " linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Questions"
notes "'Good' version of this node; 'Ask away.'"
{
NPCText "Make it quick."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about Sandover." linkto "Node_Sandover"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me a little about yourself." linkto "Node_SamHistory"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Never mind. I’ll have a look around for myself. " linkto "-1"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Oswald"
notes ""
{
NPCText "He’s the best doctor I ever met, whatever that’s worth. Works like a dog, but every day there’s more coming down sick, and we ain’t exactly well-stocked. I wouldn’t be surprised if he drops dead from the effort one of these days."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see. Maybe I can help." linkto "Node_Work_Doc"  notes "optionally go to 15 (???) What the? -dju"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask about someone else?" linkto "Node_SandoverWho"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Well that’s tragic. I’m leaving." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_SamHistory"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Me? Not much to tell. Born on the edge of the Star, kicked out on my ass, worked the trail for a while, settled down in this dump. Met an annoying asshole. That just about brings us up to right now."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "The Star? Where's that?" linkto "Node_SamHistory2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What made you decide to settle here?" linkto "Node_SamHistory6"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What happened to your face?" linkto "Node_SamFace"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I had some other questions." linkto "Node_Questions"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_SamHistory3"
notes ""
{
NPCText "They wanted to give me shit. I wouldn’t take none. That simple."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Nothing's ever that simple. What exactly happened?" linkto "Node_Notalk"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can you show me how to get to the Star?" linkto "Node_SamHistory2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So you joined the caravan trail? " linkto "Node_SamHistory5"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How did you end up here in Sandover?" linkto "Node_SamHistory6"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "33"
notes ""
{
NPCText "I’m like that. Anything else?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That’s a pretty poor attitude you have." linkto "Node_FullofShit"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Will you answer some questions for me?" linkto "Node_6"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I need to get inside. Name a price." linkto "20"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That's it for now. Bye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_SamHistory7"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Crooks, sadists, lunatics - and that’s just the people, don’t get me started on the animals. Only thing that hates a man as much as his neighbour is this planet."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "It’s a cruel world. Let me ask you about something else." linkto "Node_Questions"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "It’s a hard existence. Is that why you settled down here?" linkto "Node_SamHistory6"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_SamHistory6"
notes ""
{
NPCText "This place is a dump, always has been; I never intended to stay. But I guess you could say I found something worth hanging around for."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_GOOD playertext "What was her name?" linkto "Node_SamHistory8"  notes " *GB\n[Int/Per]"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What did you find?" linkto "Node_Notalk"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about life on the trail, before you settled here." linkto "Node_SamHistory7"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about your home town." linkto "Node_SamHistory2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You have to end up somewhere, I guess. Back to my questions." linkto "Node_Questions"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_SamHistory8"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Not much gets past you, does it? Jezebel. She was my diamond in the rough. I met her when my caravan pulled in here to trade. After five minutes of talking I’d already agreed to stay. Caravan master didn’t like it, but I said I’d take a half of what we’d agreed on and meet up with them on the return journey."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "And you ended up staying?" linkto "Node_SamHistory9"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_SamHistory9"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Well, that was seven years ago; now Jezie’s dead, I’m an old man and I never did see that caravan again."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I’m sorry to hear about that." linkto "Node_SamHistory10"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You don’t seem too cut up about it." linkto "Node_SamHistory10"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Good for you. Let me ask something else." linkto "Node_Questions"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_SamHistory10"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Time moves on. I’ll be joining her before too long."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why? Is something wrong with you?" linkto "Node_Notalk"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I’m sorry you think that way. Let me change the subject." linkto "Node_Questions"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That’s the spirit! Now tell me something else." linkto "Node_Questions"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You’re a really fun guy to be around. I’m going." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Notalk"
notes ""
{
NPCText "[He sighs plaintively.] Look… don’t think I’m standing here because I want to talk to you. It’s a job."
 NPCFemaleText "Lady... I don't do small talk. I don't do banter. I just do my job, and that don't involve listening to you yap."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Touchy subject. Let me ask something else." linkto "Node_Questions"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Your tone is beginning to annoy me." linkto "Node_FullofShit"  notes "*BB"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I thought you might appreciate the company. I guess I was wrong." linkto "-1"  notes "(done + floater)"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Fine, asshole, I’ll leave you to your ‘job’" linkto "-1"  notes "(done + floater) *BB"
              }
}
Node "Node_SamFace"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Think it suits me? I can give you one just like it."
      options {
