Node "Node_Sandover"
notes ""
{
NPCText "You can see the place, can’t you? What’s to tell?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Where do you all come from?" linkto "Node_Sandover12"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How do you people feed yourselves?" linkto "Node_Sandover2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Are there any people around here I should know about?" linkto "Node_SandoverWho"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What’s making people sick?" linkto "Node_SandoverRads"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll level with you - this place is a dump." linkto "Node_Sandover6"  notes "*BB"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I had other questions." linkto "Node_Questions"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Sandover2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Trade, mostly. Most scabs are scavengers, and there’s a lot of good salvage around here. All that electro-gizmo shit that never works, but some idiot somewhere pays for it. We spend most of the money on medical supplies."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Who is it that you trade with?" linkto "Node_Sandover3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Medical supplies are expensive. Do you make that much from scavenging?" linkto "Node_Sandover9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What do you think is causing the illness here?" linkto "Node_SandoverRads"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see. I had other questions." linkto "Node_Questions"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_SandoverWho"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Sorry bud - I don’t know what you’re used to, but Sandover ain’t too big on dignitaries. There’s Alexander, he’s in charge, and of course there’s Doc Oswald. Aside from that? We’re all just scabs."
 NPCFemaleText "Sorry missy - I don’t know what you’re used to, but Sandover ain’t too big on dignitaries. There’s Alexander, he’s in charge, and of course there’s Doc Oswald. Aside from that? We’re all just scabs."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about Alexander." linkto "60"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about Doctor Oswald." linkto "Node_Oswald"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about yourself." linkto "Node_SamHistory"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Something else…" linkto "Node_Questions"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "45"
notes ""
{
NPCText "You need it spelled out? Alright then. All scabs are rejects from the other settlements around here. For one reason or another, people get discarded, and some of ‘em end up here. That’s really all there is to it."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You’re all exiles? From where?" linkto "Node_Sandover12"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I suppose that’s how most new societies emerge. If you think about it… " linkto "Node_Notalk"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That’s all? I’ll ask another question then." linkto "Node_Questions"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I’ll be leaving now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Sandover9"
notes ""
{
NPCText "We get by, just about. When it gets bad they cut the rations of the no-hopers. Course if they did that now, they’d leave almost half the camp starving. We’ve seen better times."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see. And who do you buy your food off?" linkto "Node_Sandover3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Wow, that bad? I’m glad I’m just passing through." linkto "Node_Sandover6"  notes "(done+floater)"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Half the camp terminally ill? How long do you think this place can possibly last?" linkto "Node_Sandover7"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Haven’t we all. Back to my questions… " linkto "Node_Questions"  notes ""
              }
}
