Node "Node_SamHistory5"
notes ""
{
NPCText "I joined a caravan crew headed south. Caravaners don't give a damn who you are, as long as you can point a gun and take a beating. Spent most of my life doing just that, getting my ass beat to protect other people's shit. I saw the world. Or what's left of it, anyway."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "And you thought this would be a good place to settle down?" linkto "Node_SamHistory6"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can you show me where the Star is?" linkto "Node_SamHistory2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What a sad story. Tell me another." linkto "Node_Questions"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Sandover3"
notes "Traders actual name is 'Tech Supplies'"
{
NPCText "Not many traders'll risk coming all the way out here - recent months it's been just one lot, 'Tex Suppliers' or whatever. Bullshit name, bullshit act. Just because they're the only ones coming out here means they think they can charge whatever the hell they like."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I might be able to help. Where can I find these 'Tex Suppliers'?" linkto "53"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Well, you can't blame them for having good business sense." linkto "Node_Sandover4"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll think on that. I have another question about Sandover." linkto "Node_Sandover"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else." linkto "Node_Questions"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm leaving now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
